\c 28
\s Ahazi mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Ahazi akange ana makore makumi maviri pakutanga kwake kubata ushe; akabata ushe paJerusarema makore gumi namatanhatu; asi haana kuita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha, sababa vake Dhavhidhi;
\v 2 asi wakafamba nenzira dzamadzibaba aIsraeri, akaitira vaBhaariwo zvifananidzo zvendarira yakanyauswa.
\v 3 Uye akapisawo zvinonhuhwira pamupata womwanakomana waHinomi, akapisa vana vake mumoto, sezvainyangadza zvavahedheni, vakange vadzingwa naJehovha pamberi pavana vaIsraeri.
\v 4 Akabayira nokupisa zvinonhuhwira pamatunhu akakwirira, napazvikomo, napasi pemiti yose mitema.
\p
\v 5 Saka Jehovha Mwari wake akamuisa muruoko rwamambo weSiria; vakamukunda, vakaenda navanhu vake vazhinji vakatapwa, vakandovaisa Dhamasiko. Naiye amene akaiswa muruoko rwamambo waIsraeri, akamukunda, akauraya vazhinji-zhinji.
\v 6 nekuti Peka mwanakomana waRemaria akauraya paJudha vanhu vane zviuru zvine zana namakumi maviri pazuva rimwe; vose vari varume voumhare; nekuti vakange vasiya Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba avo.
\v 7 Zikiri murume waEfuremu, akange ane simba, akauraya Maaseya mwanakomana wamambo, naAzirikami mutariri weimba, naErikana mukuru kutevera mambo.
\p
\v 8 Vana valsiraeri vakatapa pakati pehama dzavo vanhu vane zviuru zvina mazana maviri, vakadzi, vanakomana, navanasikana, vakapambawo zvizhinji kwavari; vakandoisa Samaria izvo zvakapambwa.
\p
\v 9 Asi kwakange kuno muporofita waJehovha, wainzi Obhedhi; iye akaenda kundosangana nehondo yakange youya Samaria, akati kwavari, Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba enyu akange atsamwira vaJudha, saka akavaisa mumaoko enyu, makavauraya nehasha dzakasvikira kudenga.
\v 10 Zvino munoti muchamanikidza vana vaJudha naveJerusarema, vave vatapwa venyu varanda navarandakadzi; ko imwi hamune mhosvawo mumene pamberi paJehovha Mwari wenyu here?
\v 11 Naizvozvo zvino chindinzwai, mudzose vatapwa vamakatapa pakati pehama dzenyu; nekuti Jehovha akutsamwirai kwazvo.
\p
\v 12 Ipapo vamwe vakuru vavana vaEfuremu, vaiti: Azaria mwanakomana waJohwanani, naBherekia mwanakomana waMeshiremoti, naJehizikia mwanakomana waSharumi, naAmasa mwanakomana waHadhirai, vakadzivisa avo vabva pakurwa,
\v 13 vakati kwavari, Hamungapindi pano navatapwa, nekuti munovavarira kuita chinhu chichatiparisa mhaka pana Jehovha, mugowedzera pazvivi zvedu nemhosva yedu; nekuti mhosva yedu ihuru, vaIsraeri vatsamwirwa kwazvo naJehovha.
\p
\v 14 Ipapo varwi vakasiya vatapwa nezvakapambwa kumachinda neungano yose.
\p
\v 15 Zvino ava varume varehwa mazita avo, vakasimuka, vakatora vatapwa, vakafukidza vose vakange vakashama pakati pavo nezvakapambwa, vakavapfekedza nokuvaisa shangu, ndokuvapa zvokudya nezvokumwa, vakavazodza, vakatasvisa vose vakange vasine simba pambongoro, vakavaisa Jeriko, guta remichindwe, kuhama dzavo; ipapo vakadzokera Samaria.
\p
\v 16 Panguva iyo mambo Ahazi akatuma shoko kumadzibaba aAsiria, kuti vamubatsire.
\v 17 Nekuti vaEdhomu vakange vasvikazve, vakakunda vaJudha vakatapa vatapwa.
\v 18 NavaFirisitiawo vakange vavamba maguta amapani, naaiva kurutivi rwezasi rwaJudha, vakakunda Bhetishemeshi, neAijaroni, neGedheroti, neSoko, nemisha yawo, neTimina, nemisha yaro, neGimizo nemisha yaro; vakagarapo.
\v 19 Nekuti Jehovha akaninipisa vaJudha nokuda kwaAhazi mambo waIsraeri; nekuti akange aita zvakaipa paJudha, akatadzira Jehovha kwazvo.
\v 20 Zvino Tirigatipirineseri mambo weAsiria akauya kuzorwa naye, akamumanikidza, asi haana kumukunda.
\p
\v 21 Nekuti Ahazi akatora mugove wefuma paimba yaJehovha, napaimba yamambo, neyamachinda, akazvipa mambo weAsiria; asi hazvina kumubatsira.
\v 22 Asi panguva yokutambudzika kwake, akanyanya kutadzira Jehovha, iye mambo Ahazi.
\v 23 nekuti akabayira vamwari veDhamasiko, vakange vamukunda, akati, Vamwari vamadzimambo aSiria zvavanovabatsira, ini ndichavabayirawo, kuti vandibatsirewo. Asi ivo vakamuparadza iye navalsiraeri vose pamwechete naye.
\v 24 Zvino Ahazi akaunganidza midziyo yeimba yaMwari akaputsanya midziyo yeimba yaMwari, akapfiga mikova yeimba yaJehovha; akazviitira aritari pose-pose paJerusarema.
\v 25 Akaitawo matunhu akakwirira paguta rimwe nerimwe raJudha kuzopisira vamwe vamwari zvinonhuhwira ipapo, akatsamwisa Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba ake.
\p
\v 26 Zvino mamwe mabasa ake, netsika dzake dzose, dzokutanga nedzokupedzisira, tarirai zvakanyorwa mubhuku yamadzimambo aJudha naIsraeri.
\v 27 Ahazi akarara namadzibaba ake, vakamuviga muguta, imo muJerusarema; nekuti havana kumuisa pamarinda amadzimambo aIsraeri; Hezekia mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
